{
  "id": "adv_group_mna_01_13",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈 01 13",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "断った！？　なんでそんないい話を断ったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You turned it down?! Why would you turn down such a good offer?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 4.767414903640747,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……三枝さんも了承してくれたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saegusa-san approved of my decision.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.966666666666667,
      "endTime": 7.366666571299235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "どうして、そんなことするの？\n私に相談もなしに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why would you do something like that?\nWithout even consulting me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.566666666666666,
      "endTime": 11.666666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "話したら、麻奈は絶対やるって言うだろ\nだから、俺が独断で決めたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I’d told you‚ you would’ve definitely agreed to do it.\nSo I decided on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.866666666666667,
      "endTime": 17.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "何、それ……\n……それでも、マネージャーなの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unbelievable…\n….And you call yourself my manager?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.5,
      "endTime": 23.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.266666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーだから、断ったんだ！\nお前は今、病院に入院してるんだぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I declined BECAUSE I’m your manager!\nRight now‚ you’re in the hospital.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.266666666666666,
      "endTime": 28.166666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "こんなの明日には退院できるってお医者さんも\n言ってたよ！　ギリギリ間に合うでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the doctor said I could leave tomorrow.\nWe’ll be able to make it‚ won’t we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.4,
      "endTime": 33.900000000000006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "レイーズは大きな会場だし、あそこなら\nもっと沢山のファンに私の歌を届け――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Reyes is a big venue.\nThere‚ I could reach even more fans‚ and――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.1,
      "endTime": 39.33712015151978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いいかげんにしろ！\n長瀬麻奈は一人で歌ってるとでも思ってるのか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s enough!\nMana‚ do you think you’re singing alone?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 44.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "えっ……\n{user}……くん……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh…?\n{user}…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5,
      "endTime": 47.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "俺にならいくら迷惑をかけてもいい\nだけど、どれだけのスタッフがお前を支えている？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it were just me‚ you can cause all the trouble you want.\nBut do you know how many staff members are supporting you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.03333333333333,
      "endTime": 54.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "営業、広報、会場の手配、照明、スタイリスト……\n何十、場合によっては何百の人が関わってるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s sales‚ marketing‚ venue arrangements‚ lighting‚ stylists…\nThere are dozens‚ in some cases hundreds of people are involved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.166666666666664,
      "endTime": 64.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-mna007.m4a",
      "text": "……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.43333333333334,
      "endTime": 66.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それに、お前に万一のことがあったら、俺は\n麻奈の家族にどう詫びればいいんだ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And if something were to happen to you…\nhow could I ever apologize to your family?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.46666666666667,
      "endTime": 75.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "頼む、分かってくれ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please understand my situation…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.36666666666666,
      "endTime": 78.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-mna008.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.26666666666667,
      "endTime": 79.4666666428248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.2666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-mna009.m4a",
      "text": "私、気付かないうちに\n{user}くんにいろいろ背負わせてたんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I should’ve realized\nI made you carry so much unknowingly .",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.66666666666667,
      "endTime": 85.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-mna010.m4a",
      "text": "でもね、聞いてほしいの\n私、少し前、女の子からファンレターもらったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I want you to listen to me.\nA little while ago‚ I received a fan letter from a girl.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.5,
      "endTime": 95.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……そんなの\n麻奈ならもう何千通ももらってるだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But you’ve received\nthousands of those‚ Mana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 100.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-mna011.m4a",
      "text": "その子ね、重い病気で\n私のライブに来られないんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But this girl is suffering from a severe illness‚\nand she can’t come to my lives.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.7,
      "endTime": 105.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "え……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.93333333333334,
      "endTime": 106.65333335002263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-mna012.m4a",
      "text": "だから、テレビやブルーレイを観ながら\n一人で私を応援してるんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She sees my lives on TV and Blu-ray‚\nand roots for me all by herself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.86666666666666,
      "endTime": 112.39999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-mna013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、手紙の最後にこう書いてあったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At the end of her letter she wrote this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.6,
      "endTime": 115.95999994277953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-mna014.m4a",
      "text": "いつか、きっとライブに行くからって……\n死んじゃう前に、這ってでも行くからって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Someday she will come to my live…\nBefore she die‚ even if she has to crawl‚ she will come.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.16666666666667,
      "endTime": 123.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_13-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "その子はそこまで、麻奈を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You must mean a lot to her…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.96666666666667,
      "endTime": 126.39999999999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.966666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
